Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:36.08,Title,,0,0,0,,Many Future Paths!!\NThe Circumstances Everyone Bears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm breaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go out with someone like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani and I are breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that is the very reason Otani is fed up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what the heck were thinking leaving your boyfriend behind,{??}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Was my account inaccurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Figure it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep apologizing, I'm sure he'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to cheat on him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That really was the wrong thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a limit to my stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for going out with that other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do anything that stupid ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go out as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't break up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! A man never goes back on his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to act all macho now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This only happened because you did something you shouldn't have, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm apologizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that can be fixed with an apology, and things that can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a stranger to me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...\NThis is all a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since that last happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's really over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, I'm sorry I said such cruel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The whispering of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you asked me to come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home! I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going to break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, for how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,FOLEVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The future doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm breaking up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry about her so much that I can't concentrate on my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you break up, won't you still worry about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he was that stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is an important time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't bother him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're just going to leave it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who helped me with the Hokkaido problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but it's okay. Thing are already over between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the time to make it, so it's still okay to give it to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.94,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otani Atsushi-sama, I support you in your test efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koizumi Risa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's from Risa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:22.16,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:22.16,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice! It looks really warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on, A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.37,Superscript,,0,0,0,,PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:30.47,Superscript,,0,0,0,,OTANI FOR LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Recycled, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan sure is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't she come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Otani accepted my support package?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san, are you getting off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're still working, Kohori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the boss asked for your availability for December.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,December...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be all alone this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san, do you want to come in to work on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all going to get together and have a party after we close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come too, Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsubara-san will be there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the old lady got really drunk last year and went completely wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about "the old lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking out the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Koizumi-san, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just on my way home from prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys already broke up, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are short. How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 158 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way! I'm 2 cm shorter than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww! What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me. This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking Koizumi while she was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only because she looked so beautiful while she was sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lord! Don't say something so embarrassing out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not embarrassing! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Cram it, you midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 2 cm taller than you, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?! And besides, just what do you want with Koizumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he did with the coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.\NAs long as he's doing his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas without Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Koizumi Risa, and I'll be singing an Umibouzu song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. Can't be helped. Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Otani would usually break in and interject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd always make a silly face and shout "Yeah!" right around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan, want some Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take a break once in a while, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Christmas, after all. Why don't you spend it with Risa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her near the station not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She was with a boy around your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could go on being normal without Otani,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just no good without Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure fall over a lot for someone with such a big body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too sure about the recycled aspect of it, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you finish with your exams, I'm going to ask you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm persistent, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you dump me, or say you're breaking up with me, I'm not going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So just focus on the entrance exams for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that I said we'd break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But... your exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to like you more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make weird noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to say something that nice to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't mind if we break up a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face might be hidden, but everyone can see mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. I've got "do your best" written on my back, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I didn't get you a Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you already gave me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't give you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to like you more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the best present ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we overcame that unprecedented crisis and entered the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's New Years Day and we're already late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I only slept in because you called and woke me up at some odd hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be sad if I hadn't, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are both late, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, the lovey-dovey couple is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on getting back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pray for them to break up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-senpai is being petty as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani and the others started seriously getting into pre-exam study,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Nobu-chan and I prayed for them from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to hit the sales!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, this'll go really well with that skirt you bought last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else is working so hard.\N Is it okay for us to be doing stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "us." You're the only one who still hasn't decided on any future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What course are you going to take at technical college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, if Otani is going to be a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...how about I become a kindergarten teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to take an exam to get into a college specializing in early childhood education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what about going into fashion design?\NYou've got a good sense of style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do like looking nice... but this and that are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, darling, I'm on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun failed the Center Exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you and Chiharu-chan won't be able to go to the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sick the day of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He took too much cold medicine, and couldn't remember anything from about halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So... that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for breaking my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, last year we decided to visit a university,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and went to their festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come have some fun with us?\NWhat year are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I'm still a high school senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you going to apply here next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great having a cute girl like you come to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She's already got a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,College is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots and lots of guys came and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So many... There were so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to whichever school you go to, so do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to give up on your first-choice school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I want to be with you, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lower yourself to my level and change your first choice university,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't know if I can get in anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Suzuki-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When Chiharu-chan is willing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are other guys who could protect you at college in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tanaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi-Chiharu-chan that's dangerou—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to the same school just so you can protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you say I can replace you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying you're not confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She got pretty angry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you two just go to the same school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for her own good, and for my good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see it. That book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a literature professor who Tanaka-san really respects...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...teaching at that university.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So to give up her first choice school for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think when she works out what she really wants to do in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...she'll regret not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you said those things deliberately, Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you try to act cool like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's completely the wrong way to show her you care about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Why not just tell her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She would've been much happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You were being considerate of me to that extent...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep studying, and get into the same school as you next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...so please wait for me until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Chiharu-chan, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You've been sighing for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm the only one who hasn't decided on anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After watching those two today, I realized I really need to decide now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that when I work out what I really want to do in the future, I won't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Work that brain of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to get yours into gear too for your exam prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So time passed quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and now the entrance exams are already tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! What the heck am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This house has been infected by a level five virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Level...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and sister are both feverish and sick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This house is under quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an exam tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Take that and flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and stay at a healthy friend's house for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, I'm praying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait... I have an exam tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best in the exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's already time for graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, this isn't the time to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late for graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Final episode: Together Forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.63,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Together Forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch.
